<html>
<head>
  <style>
    html {
      font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
    }

    p {
      color: #170052;
    }

    .button {
      color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #170052;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 400;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      background-color: #170052;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      width:25%;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
        <p>We are excited to have you join us. To reset the password, please verify your email address
          using the following code.</p>
        <p style="margin: 30px 0px;" class="button">{{otp}}</p>
        <p>This code will expire in 2 hours.</p>
        <p>Cheers,</p>
        <p>Protocall Team</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>
